1. Moja sestra se druži sa *dečkom* iz srednje škole. (My sister hangs out with *a boy* from high school.)
2. Juče sam videla *dečka* koji je izgubio novčanik. (Yesterday I saw *a boy* who lost his wallet.)
3. Moja drugarica se svađala sa svojim *dečkom* juče. (My friend had an argument with her *boyfriend* yesterday.)
4. Ovo je slika moga *dečka* koju mi je poslao. (This is a picture of my *boyfriend* that he sent me.)
5. *Dečko* koji je pobedio na takmičenju bio je iznenađen. (The *boy* who won the competition was surprised.)
6. U parku sam videla *dečke* koji su igrali fudbal. (I saw *boys* playing soccer in the park.)
7. Moja sestra je otišla u bioskop sa svojim *dečkom* sinoć. (My sister went to the movies with her *boyfriend* last night.)
8. Ovaj *dečak* je veoma talentovan u slikanju. (This *boy* is very talented in painting.)
9. *Dečaci* u razredu su pravili buku tokom časa. (The *boys* in the class were making noise during the lesson.)
10. Prošle godine sam kupila novu jaknu svom *dečku*. (Last year I bought a new jacket for my *boyfriend*.)